{"tid":1655054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(hkdi同學仔召喚)cctv係要哂所有位置同時間嘅片！","createTime":"2019-10-15T01:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T01:38:19.000Z","uid":129988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b2a59f5fe053df83d2bda208e3eae2012fc623","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:26:27.000Z","msg":"先唔講班仆街有冇剪片！<br />\n我地唔可以俾佢地帶住走！<br />\n萬一出事嘅唔係佢俾我地嘅位置就冇撚意思！<br />\n所以今日去拎片嘅人！<br />\n一定要哂所有片！<br />\n仲有一樣！<br />\nmark低哂學校所有cam位置！<br />\n我地要哂咁多個位置！<br />\n唔好俾佢地拆走個cam就當從來都冇個位置嘅cctv!<br />\n<br />\n你要改同我改哂全部片！<br />\n還我真相！<br />\n還陳同學一個交待！<br />\n<br />\n同我推上去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(頭先冇寫明hkdi再開過！<br />\n仲有巴打提議要成個星期！<br />\n以免敵人帶風向，其實係第二日死！<br />\n總之我地要哂！)"},{"pid":"50c71cba16ef2be297d367377f2592c67e8d092a","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"重開！"},{"pid":"a5e49a1ec06f9dce83b1827388f66df79967d30d","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:27:14.000Z","msg":"重推！"},{"pid":"2d1f0766f232640abb1e063f9f14946c775e1962","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:27:25.000Z","msg":"幫推！"},{"pid":"941ca704621f971dcbcd1bf1e12e6cae1599c416","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"74a0d4db0522d551feefeeec3da99f0fb8832919","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"推到hkdi同學仔睇到！"},{"pid":"c101b53772ee7569e14f326ae34a448a79a933ba","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"入黎呀！"},{"pid":"45b413850efbb35977725651f24f416c71496ced","tid":1655054,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:28:51.000Z",